{"tid":713402,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[netflix] Cooking on high 首個大麻廚藝節目","createTime":"2018-06-22T18:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T03:18:15.000Z","uid":45903,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c4f4f70f3a2378328f2fa344fd8494ad2a4423","tid":713402,"uid":45903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/023321_0055363cf3bc175a416b429d59b7cd15.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F023321_0055363cf3bc175a416b429d59b7cd15.png&h=132438ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰show好似上咗無耐，講兩個廚師比賽用大麻煮嘢食，之後啲嘉賓會嗨住講評語，比分之前仲有個THC timeout，好頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰節目仲會介紹好多大麻知識，可以學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n［成個節目用嘅大麻都係醫療用途同埋合法嘅］<br />\n<br />\n有無人有睇？睇住啲嘉賓stone住傾計好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce382c2dcc7e41fe44b1dbdb65d083a691a2c10","tid":713402,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T23:48:46.000Z","msg":"咁撚過癮？！"},{"pid":"0daef7514e91a9d0b4ee65585385533a70b19a50","tid":713402,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633f19fdf2f8af4918079b7635ef13fbd2c3f024","tid":713402,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:13:07.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57ba3b95d6e33f5ad0de17e5ecc4a0f62529fcc","tid":713402,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"食住大麻睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}